Class FSDocumentIterator

java.lang.Object
com.salesforce.multicloudj.docstore.gcp.FSDocumentIterator
All Implemented Interfaces:
DocumentIterator
public class FSDocumentIterator extends Object implements DocumentIterator
Iterator for Firestore query results. This implementation properly manages the gRPC stream lifecycle to prevent thread leaks.
